name: Randy Szatny
description: I have a great sense of humor and can dish it out to make a sad day enjoyable. Honestly I have all that it takes to be a MAN, I don’t really need anything from my partner. Maybe in terms of circumstances there might some kind of help from each other, helping to make things right. I’m willing to help, stand side by side with my woman no matter what. It’s not all that easy meeting that rightful woman with all those qualities which I’m dreaming of but i strongly believe i would find someone special that will understand me and love me for who i am
